Melonesque (Melon-esque, as in "reminiscent of melons") is a theme for the Emacs Wiki.

* To apply the theme, [[https://www.emacswiki.org/emacs?action=browse;id=CSS;css=https://www.emacswiki.org/emacs/download/melonesque Click Here]]
* To go back to the default theme, [[https://www.emacswiki.org/emacs?action=browse;id=CSS;css=/light.css;theme= Click Here]]

== About üçâ ==

* Automatic dark / light themes
* Modern CSS, including color variables.
* Minimalistic and hopefully easy on the eyes.
* Does not play around with font sizes.
* Does not play around with animations.
* WCAG AAA compliant!

